\v 25 \add âSoÂŠ194666\add* DavidÂŠ194667, and the IsraeliÂŠ194668 eldersÂŠ194668, and the \add âtop army commandersÂŠ194670\add* were going to \add get\add* the box \add containing\add* Yahweh's agreement from the houseÂŠ194682 of Obed EdomÂŠ194685 with \add much\add* \add âcelebration\add*.
