\p Those were the LevitesÂŠ198350 listed by theirÂŠ198352 ancestors' families.
\v 31 They too, used lots just like Aharon's descendantsÂŠ198362 (their relatives) \add to determine their specific duties\add* irrespective of where theyÂŠ198357 came in their familiesÂŠ198371. This was done in frontÂŠ198365 of King DavidÂŠ198366, TsadokÂŠ198368 and Ahimelek, the clan leaders, and the \add other\add* priestsÂŠ198372 and LevitesÂŠ198373.
