\v 22 YerimotÂŠ198638 and his sonsÂŠ198639 and relativesÂŠ198640 (twelve),
\li1
\v 23 HanayahÂŠ198646 and his sonsÂŠ198647 and relativesÂŠ198648 (twelve),
