\v 24 YoshbekashahÂŠ198654 and his sonsÂŠ198655 and relativesÂŠ198656 (twelve),
\li1
\v 25 HananiÂŠ198662 and his sonsÂŠ198663 and relativesÂŠ198664 (twelve),
