\v 23 DavidÂŠ199479 didn'tÂŠ199476 include menÂŠ199481 who were less than twentyÂŠ199482 years old when he had ordered a censusÂŠ199480, because YahwehÂŠ199487 had promised that he would multiply the IsraelisÂŠ199491 like starsÂŠ199492 in the sky.\x + \xo 27:23: \xt Gen 15:5; 22:17; 26:4.\x*
